knowledgeGraph.title: OHSU Doernbecher Children's Hospital
knowledgeGraph.description: Doernbecher Children's Hospital is an academic teaching children's hospital associated with Oregon Health & Science University located in Portland, Oregon. Established in 1926, it is the first full-service children's hospital in the Pacific Northwest, and provides full-spectrum pediatric care.
